<dl id="n06054f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06054f">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06054f"> 54(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> hold doll during / operation</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Une petite fille, &hellip; &agrave; laquelle on s&apos;&eacute;tait vu oblig&eacute; de couper la jambe, <mark>avait subi toute l&apos;op&eacute;ration</mark> sans prof&eacute;rer une seule plainte, <mark>en serrant &eacute;troitement sa poup&eacute;e dans ses bras</mark>. <font color="green">[A little girl, who had been forced to cut off her leg, had undergone the whole operation without uttering a single complaint, by pressing her doll tightly in her arms.]</font> <small> Fr&eacute;d&eacute;ric Queyrat, <a name="FQLJ" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#FQLJ"><cite title="source">Les Jeux des Enfants</cite></a> (1920) 123</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c01125a" href="c01all.htm#c01125a">VI.C.01:125(a)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
